{"id":614415,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2019/07/立场新闻-操普通话男子破坏城大民主墙推倒民主/","date":"2019-07-24T13:38:58Z","modified":"2019-07-24T13:38:58Z","title":"立场新闻 | 操普通话男子破坏城大民主墙推倒民主女神像","content":"<div id=\"attachment_614416\" style=\"width: 560px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/07/67403602_10156826565871656_218330573683294208_n_3uoSL_1200x0.png\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-614416\" class=\"wp-image-614416\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/07/67403602_10156826565871656_218330573683294208_n_3uoSL_1200x0.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"367\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/07/67403602_10156826565871656_218330573683294208_n_3uoSL_1200x0.png 1200w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/07/67403602_10156826565871656_218330573683294208_n_3uoSL_1200x0-300x200.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/07/67403602_10156826565871656_218330573683294208_n_3uoSL_1200x0-768x512.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/07/67403602_10156826565871656_218330573683294208_n_3uoSL_1200x0-1024x683.png 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/07/67403602_10156826565871656_218330573683294208_n_3uoSL_1200x0-360x240.png 360w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a><p id=\"caption-attachment-614416\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">7.23 城大民主墙</p></div>\n<p>反送中运动激起社会矛盾，反修例市民在各区设的连侬墙多次成为破坏目标，城市大学学生会今日发布相片和片段，指有操普通话的人撕毁城大内民主墙上的纸条，并推倒在旁的民主女神像。</p>\n<p>片段显示有一名穿黑衣的男子，撕毁民主墙上的贴文之后，推倒民主女神像，雕像多处受损，有在场人士上前喝止，之后该男子试图离开，被在场人士阻止之后将他交予校园保安，学生会已报警处理。</p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">A man was arrested after he destroyed the Goddess of Democracy statue at CityU &amp; tore down posts from Democracy Wall. He was heard to have been speaking Mandarin. <a href=\"https://t.co/vMoQXrCLdh\">pic.twitter.com/vMoQXrCLdh</a></p>\n<p>&mdash; Kong 